original: Lindstedt, Carl-Eric Natanael, kyrkoherde, Vinköl, f. 31/10/94 i Järpås, Skarab. 1. G. 21 m. Stina Jonsson, i Barn: Elisabet f. 22, Birgitta 23, Monica 28, Per-Nathan 30. — Stud:’ex. i Skara 13, teol. fil. ex. i Gbg 14, teol. kand. i Lund 19, prästex. i Skara 20. Kommin. i Larv 21, i Lidköp. 26, las:-pred. 26, kyrkoh. i Vinköl fr. 28. Ordf. i Vinköls o. Marums kyrkostämmor, i skolråd. Skr.: stiftskrön. i Skara stifts julbok ett flert. år.
translated: Lindstedt, Carl-Eric Natanael, parish priest, Vinköl, b. 31/10/94 in Järpås, Skaraborg. 1st marriage: Married on 21 with Stina Jonsson, they had the following children: Elisabet b. 22, Birgitta b. 23, Monica b. 28, Per-Nathan b. 30. — Education: Gymnasium in Skara in 13, Bachelor of Theology in Gothenburg in 14, Candidacy in Theology in Lund in 19, Ordination Examination in Skara in 20. Assistant priest in Larv in 21, in Lidköping in 26, church preacher in 26, parish priest in Vinköl from 28. Chairman of Vinköl and Marum's church assemblies, in the school council. Writings: Diocesan chronicle in Skara diocese's Christmas book multiple years.

works.name: Diocesan chronicle in Skara diocese's Christmas book
